Ayah yang ajar saya sewaktu kecil.

92
00:06:07,679 --> 00:06:08,720
Ia pasti berkesan.

93
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:13,920
Dah selesai.

94
00:06:14,119 --> 00:06:15,519
Cik muda, apakah perasaan awak?

95
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,600
Saya seakan-akan tak begitu sakit.

96
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,119
Liu Ying, hebatnya awak!

97
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,040
Bagusnya.

98
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:24,160
Cik muda dapat menghadiri
Jamuan Sanggul Bunga dengan cantik.

99
00:06:26,335 --> 00:06:27,200
(Jumpa Naga Dalam Seribu Tahun)

100
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:30,799
Jangan begitu hargai

101
