seperti kita nampaknya?

104
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:40,079
Cik muda, gerak-geri naga
begitu misteri.

105
00:06:40,359 --> 00:06:41,600
Barangkali saya dapat

106
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:43,799
