Cik muda, tengoklah!

109
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,720
Memang ada naga!

110
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,040
Ya, ada.

111
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:03,119
Awak boleh kahwin dengan naga
