Balik ke rumah.

153
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,359
Kenapakah awak balik lagi?

154
00:12:40,599 --> 00:12:42,159
Awak nak hadiahkan bunga kepada saya?

155
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:46,640
Rupa-rupanya, awak nak tukar
kuih Osmanthus dengan saya.

156
00:12:52,119 --> 00:12:54,960
(Terdapat aroma segar pada manusia ini.)

157
00:12:55,159 --> 00:12:56,679
(Selesanya.)

158
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,479
Jangan takut.

159
00:13:35,359 --> 00:13:37,799
Raja Naga, kenapakah
awak datang ke sini?

160
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:46,200
