Perisai Emas? Cari maut!

161
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:00,760
(Nak sekat saya?)

162
00:16:08,280 --> 00:16:10,000
Cik muda, jalan perlahan-lahan.

163
00:16:16,039 --> 00:16:17,520
Tak sangka Lembah Luo Ying
di gunung belakang kita

164
00:16:17,679 --> 00:16:18,840
