165
00:16:19,239 --> 00:16:20,640
Saya seakan-akan bermimpi.

166
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:22,039
Ya.

167
00:16:23,239 --> 00:16:24,599
Indah sangat.

168
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:30,960
Cik muda, ada banyak bunga
yang telah gugur di sini.

169
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,039
Cik muda.

170
00:16:37,239 --> 00:16:38,320
