Cik muda, jangan takut.

175
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:56,840
Saya pergi tengok.

176
00:16:57,039 --> 00:16:58,000
Jalan perlahan-lahan.

177
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:36,479
Cik muda!

178
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,640
Kenapa?

179
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,319
Cik muda, sana...

180
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,479
Ada ular di sana.

181
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:41,560
Ular?

182
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,400
